title: 22 (Taylor's Version)
description:
Taylor Swift took back the power and made her 22nd birthday a great one since we all know how her 21st birthday turned out. Amy, Ana, Nick and Lacey break down this fun song, and discuss all the jabs that she has made to that particular ex. And what was up with all of the 2022 stuff?
Plus, thanks so much to Sarah for making these perfect concert playlists! Check out Lacey's perfect concert here- https://open.spotify.com/playlist/3w1vyBWhxhDczgi3FRy5va?si=QDnu9Sm5QBWJalZ6CpQsuw&nd=1.
Nick's perfect concert playlist is here- https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5GRocCzZPXoli2sOGUGzhY?si=s-Pgag15Q1q3NBrV4arfUg

What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us and we love hearing from you all!
